Sentencas: Fast and accurate parameter extraction of fuel cells is crucial to the control and performance analysis of fuel cell power systems.
Titulo: Fast, and accurate parameter extraction for different types of fuel cells with decomposition and nature-inspired optimization method

Sentencas: Unfortunately, due to the multivariable and nonlinear features of fuel cell models, it is a difficult task to identify the parameters of the models.
Titulo: Fast, and accurate parameter extraction for different types of fuel cells with decomposition and nature-inspired optimization method

Sentencas: In this paper, we propose a decomposition technique, where the unknown parameters are divided into two groups: nonlinear and linear.
Titulo: Fast, and accurate parameter extraction for different types of fuel cells with decomposition and nature-inspired optimization method

Sentencas: The optimization techniques only need to optimize the nonlinear parameters, and then the linear parameters are determined based on the nonlinear ones.
Titulo: Fast, and accurate parameter extraction for different types of fuel cells with decomposition and nature-inspired optimization method

Sentencas: With the help of the decomposition technique, a generalized framework by using the nature-inspired optimization method is proposed to try to fast and accurately extract the parameters for different types of fuel cells.
Titulo: Fast, and accurate parameter extraction for different types of fuel cells with decomposition and nature-inspired optimization method

Sentencas: To test the performances of our approach, two widely used types of fuel cells are studied, i.e., proton exchange membrane fuel cell and solid oxide fuel cell.
Titulo: Fast, and accurate parameter extraction for different types of fuel cells with decomposition and nature-inspired optimization method

Sentencas: Extensive simulation tests with thirty-two instances are carried out for comparing our approach with existing approaches.
Titulo: Fast, and accurate parameter extraction for different types of fuel cells with decomposition and nature-inspired optimization method

Sentencas: The comparison demonstrates the efficiency of the decomposition technique.
Titulo: Fast, and accurate parameter extraction for different types of fuel cells with decomposition and nature-inspired optimization method

Sentencas: Moreover, the results show that our approach can not only significantly reduce the computational resources, but also yields high quality solutions.
Titulo: Fast, and accurate parameter extraction for different types of fuel cells with decomposition and nature-inspired optimization method
